{"tid":2021771,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(耐人尋味) 郭文貴獨家公布海航劉呈杰照片","createTime":"2020-05-18T02:52:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-18T12:43:59.000Z","uid":184679,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b3a611eb1d5a68ea394543305370b600f3c34081","tid":2021771,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T02:52:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/aAlV2qjofBkWnIPXd7aGJQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTEyNDI7aD04MjcuNzczMjc0OTE3ODUzMg--/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/btQ5bd5tOecp2TPdbqNMHw--~B/aD0xMjE3O3c9MTgyNjtzbT0xO2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/cmmedia.com.tw/10bb2bb224603f15646613d7b857658a\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FaAlV2qjofBkWnIPXd7aGJQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTEyNDI7aD04MjcuNzczMjc0OTE3ODUzMg--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FbtQ5bd5tOecp2TPdbqNMHw--~B%2FaD0xMjE3O3c9MTgyNjtzbT0xO2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fko%2Fcmmedia.com.tw%2F10bb2bb224603f15646613d7b857658a&h=ec541096&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（圖片來源／翻攝G news）<br />\n<br />\n中國駐以色列大使杜偉在床上猝死、國家院士鍾南山向美國有線電視新聞網《CNN》承認武漢當局在肺炎最開始隱瞞疫情、大量解放軍出現在福建平潭，中國兩會與台灣總統就職520前夕，這麼多的騷動之下郭文貴加碼爆料，國家副總理王岐山已被軟禁近40天，還有更猛的，公布海航集團洗錢受益人之一的劉呈杰照片，所有網友一看就認定是「他」的私生子。<br />\n<br />\n郭文貴自2015年逃出中國，忍到2017年上美國之音爆料之後，多次舉發中國海南航空集團洗錢，一家國有公司蒐集財富之後，大量舉債，CEO王健被謀殺，再私有化到貫君、孫姚、劉呈杰幾個大官的私生子女身上，每個人身價千億，並找來越南裔的德國前副總理菲利普&bull;羅斯勒（Philipp R&ouml;sler）擔任基金會主持人，遇到武漢肺炎受到重創之後，再由海南省政府接回海航集團。<br />\n<br />\n過去郭文貴在爆料時，提出貫君與副總理王岐山的DNA比對表，以及貫君的照片，一口咬定貫君是王岐山的私生子，整個海航集團是上海幫江澤民、朱鎔基、王岐山的掏空中國國有銀行、掏空資產、掏空股市投資人的盜國工具，但郭文貴遲遲未公布劉呈杰的照片，15日起他的爆料平台受到中國駭客猛烈的攻擊，原來郭文貴要公布的是劉呈杰的照片。<br />\n<br />\n過去網友都猜劉呈杰是江澤民、朱鎔基、劉雲山的私生子，但照片一看，就認定是「這個人」的私生子，因為特徵實在太像，郭文貴壓了兩年才把與中國政府談判籌碼曝光，現在恍然大悟，原來海航集團的盜國計畫，「這個人」也有參與。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">中南海希望川普慘輸，解放軍已向平潭集結</span><br />\n<br />\n郭文貴16日爆料說，中國因為肺炎疫情在國際戰場上受挫，中國兩會決定加大對回收香港的力道，只會發生更殘暴的鎮壓，決議「一定要堅持到11月份看到美國民主黨贏了、川普下台為止，因為那就是共產黨贏了。」<br />\n<br />\n對台灣部分，郭文貴爆料，多個解放軍將領頻頻喊打，上書習近平「要在歷史階段做出犧牲」、「要把台灣打爛打沉」、「不讓台灣一直成為分裂祖國的芒刺」，但郭文貴以公布劉呈杰的照片示警中南海繼續爆料，「如果你們敢對香港、台灣下重手，我就連續直播10個小時」！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.mobi.yahoo.com/trendr/%E4%BF%A1%E5%82%B3%E5%AA%92/%E7%A7%81%E7%94%9F%E5%AD%90-%E9%83%AD%E6%96%87%E8%B2%B4%E7%8D%A8%E5%AE%B6%E5%85%AC%E5%B8%83%E6%B5%B7%E8%88%AA%E5%8A%89%E5%91%88%E6%9D%B0%E7%85%A7%E7%89%87-%E7%AB%9F%E7%84%B6%E8%B7%9F-%E4%BB%96-%E9%95%B7%E5%BE%97%E5%BE%88%E5%83%8F-021749886.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.mobi.yahoo.com%2Ftrendr%2F%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E5%2582%25B3%25E5%25AA%2592%2F%25E7%25A7%2581%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%25AD%2590-%25E9%2583%25AD%25E6%2596%2587%25E8%25B2%25B4%25E7%258D%25A8%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%25B8%2583%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E8%2588%25AA%25E5%258A%2589%25E5%2591%2588%25E6%259D%25B0%25E7%2585%25A7%25E7%2589%2587-%25E7%25AB%259F%25E7%2584%25B6%25E8%25B7%259F-%25E4%25BB%2596-%25E9%2595%25B7%25E5%25BE%2597%25E5%25BE%2588%25E5%2583%258F-021749886.html&d=bavYdQ8E6vkyiKAGb1dQCVSbKypX9O9wpAPGBeI%2BXHg%3D&h=66d2440d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.mobi.yahoo.com/trendr/%E4%BF%A1%E5%82%B3%E5%AA%92/%E7%A7%81%E7%94%9F%E5%AD%90-%E9%83%AD%E6%96%87%E8%B2%B4%E7%8D%A8%E5%AE%B6%E5%85%AC%E5%B8%83%E6%B5%B7%E8%88%AA%E5%8A%89%E5%91%88%E6%9D%B0%E7%85%A7%E7%89%87-%E7%AB%9F%E7%84%B6%E8%B7%9F-%E4%BB%96-%E9%95%B7%E5%BE%97%E5%BE%88%E5%83%8F-021749886.html</a>"},{"pid":"b4c5df6ce8953b8b47b8baa92f5f2c47cf627a8d","tid":2021771,"uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T02:56:13.000Z","msg":"那位先生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93d82f022e67590de14f2fe26f90c93c45ae0ced","tid":2021771,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T03:17:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Winnie2.0？？？</span></span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b02de9baacb44bf5c3e6ce1fa002dea1f4c701b9","tid":2021771,"uid":53003,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T03:19:21.000Z","msg":"呢啲就有圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n范冰冰呢？"},{"pid":"086fdd430ff4ae0fe89c5f96968e193b9afed601","tid":2021771,"uid":49359,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T03:31:36.000Z","msg":"佛地魔?<br />\n成篇文唔敢講個名"},{"pid":"c5d00dc7e312c2a430922120ca6e444b7791b86e","tid":2021771,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"b02de9baacb44bf5c3e6ce1fa002dea1f4c701b9","tid":2021771,"uid":53003,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T03:19:21.000Z","msg":"呢啲就有圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n范冰冰呢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T03:32:14.000Z","msg":"含撚片呢"},{"pid":"d8be6d39d74b29c3acec35854d20cc5fb65d7cce","tid":2021771,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T03:32:51.000Z","msg":"想知既又唔見佢爆料"},{"pid":"131eb2c18428b8a21e3dca90eaf49b984a523afb","tid":2021771,"uid":268516,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T03:57:54.000Z","msg":"又話跳樓嘅？"},{"pid":"9dd2493d6cc02338d5c07b015f454ba4533cb9cc","tid":2021771,"uid":37525,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"086fdd430ff4ae0fe89c5f96968e193b9afed601","tid":2021771,"uid":49359,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T03:31:36.000Z","msg":"佛地魔?<br />\n成篇文唔敢講個名"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T04:52:35.000Z","msg":"甴近平？<br />\n但係仔似老母<br />\n唔會同維尼餅印先係喎"},{"pid":"bd5eb9e8207e6fdef0a856e7377360b51e4860f1","tid":2021771,"uid":33263,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b3a611eb1d5a68ea394543305370b600f3c34081","tid":2021771,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T02:52:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/aAlV2qjofBkWnIPX